---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import MetaballButton from '../components/MetaballButton.astro';
---
<Base
  description="A brand identity studio for boutique movement and wellness operators — closing the gap between who you are when you teach and how you look online."
>

<div class="panel-stack">

<!-- ── 01 HERO ───────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="s-hero panel" style="z-index:1">

  <div class="hero-body">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow r">// RESONANCE.OS — BRAND IDENTITY FOR MOVEMENT &amp; WELLNESS</p>
    <h1 class="hero-h1 diag-h">
      <span class="diag-line">Clients meet you</span>
      <span class="diag-line">in person.</span>
      <span class="diag-line">They don't recognize</span>
      <span class="diag-line">you online.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub r" data-d="1">A brand identity studio for boutique movement and wellness operators. We close the gap between who you are when you teach and how you come across on a screen.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas r" data-d="2">
      <MetaballButton href="/id" label="Start your ID — €247" />
      <MetaballButton href="/site" variant="ghost" label="Explore Resonance.SITE" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Spline logo animation -->
  <div class="spline-wrap">
    <spline-viewer url="https://prod.spline.design/SSUb1QPOv-tdYAa2/scene.splinecode" loading="lazy"></spline-viewer>
  </div>

  <!-- Brand dashboard preview slides in below -->
  <aside class="vault-card r" data-d="3">
    <header class="vault-card-hd">
      <span class="vault-card-eyebrow">// Resonance.ID · Brand Vault</span>
      <span class="vault-card-status">Live</span>
    </header>
    <div class="vault-card-swatches" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="vault-card-sw" style="background:#f9f9f9"></span>
      <span class="vault-card-sw" style="background:#f0eee9"></span>
      <span class="vault-card-sw" style="background:#d4cfc9"></span>
      <span class="vault-card-sw" style="background:#f75b1d"></span>
      <span class="vault-card-sw" style="background:#222222"></span>
    </div>
    <hr class="vault-card-divider" />
    <p class="vault-card-section">// Recommended tagline</p>
    <blockquote class="vault-card-quote">"Where your body finds its frequency."</blockquote>
    <p class="vault-card-why">Fits both studio and product narratives — recommended by the system.</p>
    <footer class="vault-card-foot">
      <span>7 modules</span><span class="sep">·</span>
      <span>Aa Urbanist</span><span class="sep">·</span>
      <span>#F75B1D</span><span class="sep">·</span>
      <span>ID System v3</span>
    </footer>
  </aside>

</section>


<!-- ── 02 THE GAP ──────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="s panel panel--alt" id="gap" style="z-index:2">
  <span class="lbl r">// THE GAP</span>
  <h2 class="h2 diag-h r" data-d="1">
    <span class="diag-line">The room you hold</span>
    <span class="diag-line">doesn't survive</span>
    <span class="diag-line">the trip to your website.</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="body-lg gap-body r" data-d="2">The brand lives in how you teach, what you notice, the way you set up a room. It lives in your voice on a Sunday morning when you talk about it. Your Instagram already carries some of it — it looks five times better than your website, and you know it. The website is the version you wrote in an evening, between sessions, on a template that wasn't built for you. That's the gap. We rebuild the website from the brand — not the other way around.</p>
</section>


<!-- ── 03 WHY — FLOEMA EDITORIAL LIST ─────────────── -->
<section class="s panel panel--dark" id="why" style="z-index:3">
  <span class="lbl r">// A DIFFERENT KIND OF STUDIO</span>
  <h2 class="h2 diag-h r" data-d="1">
    <span class="diag-line">Three reasons</span>
    <span class="diag-line">we're not the agency</span>
    <span class="diag-line">you've been quoted by.</span>
  </h2>

  <div class="editorial-list">
    <div class="editorial-item r" data-d="1">
      <span class="editorial-n">01</span>
      <div class="editorial-body">
        <p class="editorial-h diag-h">
          <span class="diag-line">Built around recognition,</span>
          <span class="diag-line">not deliverables.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="editorial-p">Most studios sell you a logo, a palette, and a 40-page guide. We sell the moment you read your own brand back and think <em style="font-style:normal;color:var(--ink)">yes, that's me</em>. The palette, the tagline, the website — those are just the proof.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="editorial-item r" data-d="2">
      <span class="editorial-n">02</span>
      <div class="editorial-body">
        <p class="editorial-h diag-h">
          <span class="diag-line">Built to be</span>
          <span class="diag-line">useful in 30 seconds.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="editorial-p">Discovery, workshops, presentations, revisions. Most agencies use the same six weeks we use to deliver the entire Resonance.ID. You answer 12 questions. Your dashboard is generated. You read it the same evening.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="editorial-item r" data-d="3">
      <span class="editorial-n">03</span>
      <div class="editorial-body">
        <p class="editorial-h diag-h">
          <span class="diag-line">Built for one</span>
          <span class="diag-line">specific market.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="editorial-p">We do not work with fintech founders. We do not work with B2B SaaS. We work with people who teach movement. The intake is tuned for it. The voice rules are tuned for it. The blueprint is tuned for it. That's why it lands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ── 04 TWO WAYS IN — PRODUCT OVERVIEW ───────────── -->
<section class="s panel panel--alt" id="products" style="z-index:4">
  <span class="lbl r">// TWO WAYS IN</span>
  <h2 class="h2 diag-h r" data-d="1">
    <span class="diag-line">Start with the brand.</span>
    <span class="diag-line">Add the site</span>
    <span class="diag-line">when you're ready.</span>
  </h2>

  <div class="prod-cards">
    <a class="prod-card r" data-d="2" href="/id">
      <span class="prod-card-lbl">// RESONANCE.ID</span>
      <h3 class="prod-card-ttl">Your brand, in one dashboard.</h3>
      <p class="prod-card-desc">A complete brand identity — seven modules, written from your own words, set in your palette and type. Delivered as a private dashboard, the same day.</p>
      <span class="prod-card-meta">€247 · about 20 minutes</span>
      <span class="prod-card-go">Explore Resonance.ID <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
    </a>
    <a class="prod-card r" data-d="3" href="/site">
      <span class="prod-card-lbl">// RESONANCE.SITE</span>
      <h3 class="prod-card-ttl">The website, rebuilt from the brand.</h3>
      <p class="prod-card-desc">A full Astro build on top of your ID. Up to four pages, two weeks to live — for the moment something is changing and the old site has stopped matching you.</p>
      <span class="prod-card-meta">from €3,500 · ID credited in full</span>
      <span class="prod-card-go">Explore Resonance.SITE <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ── 05 PROJECTS ─────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="s panel" id="projects" style="z-index:5">
  <span class="lbl r">// PROJECTS</span>
  <div class="project-list">
    <details class="project-accordion r" data-d="1">
      <summary class="project-row">
        <span class="project-num">01</span>
        <span class="project-name">KRAFTT</span>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span class="project-badge">ID</span>
          <span class="project-loc">KRAFTT Movement · Amsterdam</span>
        </div>
        <span class="project-expand" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="project-case">
        <div class="project-case-grid">
          <div class="project-case-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="project-case-visual-lbl">Case study · in progress</span>
          </div>
          <div class="project-case-copy">
            <p class="project-case-lbl">// THE BRIEF</p>
            <p class="project-case-h">A movement studio repositioning around teacher training.</p>
            <p class="project-case-p">KRAFTT came in with the studio already running. The brief: rebuild the brand so the next chapter — a teacher training that starts in autumn — could sit underneath one voice.</p>
            <p class="project-case-p">Resonance.ID captured the studio voice in a single evening. The recommended tagline was used in the next Instagram post the same week. Site build follows in Q3.</p>
            <div class="project-case-meta">
              <span><strong>Stage</strong> · ID delivered</span>
              <span><strong>Studio</strong> · KRAFTT Movement</span>
              <span><strong>Location</strong> · Amsterdam</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="project-accordion r" data-d="2">
      <summary class="project-row">
        <span class="project-num">02</span>
        <span class="project-name">PMB</span>
        <div class="project-meta">
          <span class="project-badge">ID</span>
          <span class="project-loc">Pilates Movement Berlin · Berlin</span>
        </div>
        <span class="project-expand" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="project-case">
        <div class="project-case-grid">
          <div class="project-case-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="project-case-visual-lbl">Case study · in progress</span>
          </div>
          <div class="project-case-copy">
            <p class="project-case-lbl">// THE BRIEF</p>
            <p class="project-case-h">A pilates studio outgrowing its first website.</p>
            <p class="project-case-p">PMB had three years of teaching, a strong Instagram, and a website that read like a placeholder. The intake produced a brand vault that finally matched the room.</p>
            <p class="project-case-p">The voice rules — particular, unhurried, direct — went straight into the next class description rewrite. Site is in scoping.</p>
            <div class="project-case-meta">
              <span><strong>Stage</strong> · ID delivered</span>
              <span><strong>Studio</strong> · Pilates Movement Berlin</span>
              <span><strong>Location</strong> · Berlin</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <div class="project-row project-row--ph r" data-d="3">
      <span class="project-num">03</span>
      <span class="project-name">More coming soon</span>
    </div>
    <div class="project-row project-row--ph r" data-d="4">
      <span class="project-num">04</span>
      <span class="project-name">Your studio could be here</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ── 06 THE STUDIO ───────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="s panel panel--alt" id="studio" style="z-index:6">
  <span class="lbl r">// THE STUDIO</span>
  <h2 class="h2 diag-h r" data-d="1" style="margin-bottom:2rem">
    <span class="diag-line">One person,</span>
    <span class="diag-line">plus a system that</span>
    <span class="diag-line">does the listening</span>
    <span class="diag-line">at scale.</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="studio-grid">
    <div class="studio-copy">
      <p class="body-lg r" data-d="2">Resonance.OS is built and run by Saja Dehaan, working between Leeuwarden and Berlin. The system reads every intake. The person reviews every output before it ships.</p>
      <p class="body r" data-d="3">The point of the studio is not to scale headcount. It's to keep one person close enough to the work that the output stays accurate — and to let the system do the listening so a brand identity doesn't cost €5,000 anymore.</p>
      <MetaballButton href="mailto:saja@resonance-os.studio?subject=Hello%20Saja" variant="ghost" icon="mail" label="Talk to Saja" class="r" data-d="4" style="align-self:flex-start;margin-top:0.5rem" />
    </div>
    <div class="studio-av r" data-d="3">
      <span class="studio-av-lbl">Saja Dehaan · Studio</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


